    Event data slice from UCDP

    ucdp.Rd

    event data from UCDP for select countries from 2001 to 2019

    Usage

    data(ucdp)

    Source

    ucdp

    References

    add ucdp reference (ucdp)

    Examples

    data(ucdp)
